" NOTE: Use `BS` to show the upper level mappings

" Map leader to which_key
nnoremap <silent> <leader> :silent <c-u> :silent WhichKey '<Space>'<CR>
vnoremap <silent> <leader> :silent <c-u> :silent WhichKeyVisual '<Space>'<CR>

